OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774400571
OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FTransgender girls who are members of
OL,7,FGirlguiding have been told they must
OL,8,Fleave by early September.
OL,10,FIt follows an announcement by the
OL,11,Forganisation in December, which stated
OL,12,Fthat transgender girls would no longer
OL,13,Fbe able to join, as it confirmed it
OL,14,Fwas limiting its membership to "girls
OL,15,Fand young women".
OL,17,FThe decision comes almost eight months
OL,18,Fafter a Supreme Court ruling which
OL,19,Fsaid the words "woman" and "sex" in
OL,20,Fthe Equality Act 2010 refer to a
OL,21,Fbiological woman and biological sex.
OL,26,@{D@POU{D@VO]{D@\OU{D@`O]
