FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774400571
OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FGirlguiding said that since that
OL,7,Fruling, it had undertaken "detailed
OL,8,Fconsiderations, expert legal advice
OL,9,Fand input from senior members, young
OL,10,Fmembers", its council and board of
OL,11,Ftrustees.
OL,13,FIn an update on Tuesday, the
OL,14,Forganisation said trans girls who are
OL,15,Fmembers can stay until September 6.
OL,17,FIt added that any trans girl or trans
OL,18,Fwoman who is currently volunteering in
OL,19,Fa role open to women only will be
OL,20,Frequired to move to a position that is
OL,21,Fopen to males or females.
OL,26,@oD@[OUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
