OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774400571
OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FIn a statement, the organisation said:
OL,7,F"Today, Girlguiding shared further
OL,8,Foperational information with our
OL,9,Fmembers about the timings for this
OL,10,Fchange.
OL,12,F"The update explained that current
OL,13,Fyoung members who are trans girls can
OL,14,Fstay with Girlguiding until 6
OL,15,FSeptember 2026.
OL,17,F"This allows affected members and
OL,18,Ftheir families time to plan, prepare,
OL,19,Faccess support, and decide when `
OL,20,Fbetween now and September ` they feel
OL,21,Fready to leave.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774400571
OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,F"Any trans girl or trans woman who is
OL,7,Fcurrently volunteering in a role open
OL,8,Fto women only, will need to move to a
OL,9,Frole that is open to all volunteers by
OL,10,F6 September 2026."
OL,12,FMembers can range in age from four to
OL,13,F18, and there are currently around
OL,14,F300,000 across the Rainbows, Brownies,
OL,15,FGuides and Rangers groups within
OL,16,FGirlguiding, as well as around 80,000
OL,17,Fvolunteers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
