OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774400571
OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FThe organisation has previously said
OL,7,Fit does not collect gender identity
OL,8,Finformation on its members and
OL,9,Ftherefore does not have numbers for
OL,10,Fhow many might be affected by the rule
OL,11,Fchange.
OL,13,FGirlguiding insisted it remains
OL,14,F"committed to standing up for the
OL,15,Frights, safety and dignity of girls
OL,16,Fand women, and to supporting
OL,17,Fmarginalised communities, including
OL,18,FLGBTQ+ people, to improve the lives of
OL,19,Fgirls".
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
