OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FIt called for the upcoming guidance on
OL,7,Fsingle-sex spaces, which was drafted
OL,8,Fby Britain's rights watchdog the
OL,9,FEquality and Human Rights Commission
OL,10,F(EHRC) and is currently being
OL,11,Fconsidered by government, to be
OL,12,F"clear, workable and informed by the
OL,13,Fvoices of young people and
OL,14,Fvolunteering organisations, to ensure
OL,15,Fthat the wellbeing of all girls
OL,16,Fremains at its heart".
