OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FCampaign group Trans+ Solidarity
OL,7,FAlliance described the news as
OL,8,F"heartbreaking for the children and
OL,9,Fvolunteer leaders that hold
OL,10,FGirlguiding together".
OL,12,FIt said: "Inclusive organisations
OL,13,Fbeing bullied into excluding people
OL,14,Fagainst their will is a profound
OL,15,Ffailure of this Government to live up
OL,16,Fto its promises to the trans
OL,17,Fcommunity."
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@UO]tD@JOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
