OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FFollowing the initial announcement
OL,7,Flast year on the change to membership,
OL,8,Fa coalition of volunteers and parents
OL,9,Fargued that refusing a child based on
OL,10,Ftheir gender identity "sends a message
OL,11,Fof rejection" to young people.
OL,13,FGuiders Against Trans Exclusion (Gate)
OL,14,Fcoordinated demonstrations in various
OL,15,FUK cities at the time.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
