OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FBut while some volunteers within
OL,7,FGirlguiding have threatened to resign
OL,8,Fover the issue, others welcomed the
OL,9,Fchange, saying they had expressed
OL,10,Fsafeguarding concerns and were pleased
OL,11,Fat the new approach.
OL,13,FIt was also announced in December that
OL,14,Ftransgender women will be banned from
OL,15,Fbecoming members of the Women's
OL,16,FInstitute from April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
