OL,3,CTransgender girls who are members of
OL,4,CGirlguiding told to leave by September
OL,6,FMaking its announcement at the time,
OL,7,Fthe National Federation of Women's
OL,8,FInstitutes (NFWI) said the decision
OL,9,Fhad been taken "with the utmost regret
OL,10,Fand sadness", adding that it retains
OL,11,Fthe "firm belief that transgender
OL,12,Fwomen are women".
OL,14,FSimilarly to Girlguiding, the NFWI
OL,15,Fsaid it does not hold data on how many
OL,16,Fof its members are transgender.
